msg: Check into trunk updates equivalent to  r1439995, r1439990,  r1439989, r1439974

author: rhuijben
msg: When the merge code detects and installs a tree conflict, the single file
merge notification handling shouldn't tell that we just skipped the file.
(single_file_merge_notify): Don't accidentally overwrite a tree conflict.
